## “Natuleya!” mu 2010
## Kuli fwebengi umwaka wafumako wali “mwaka wa nsapato ishalamba” - ukwendauka nganshi, ukushimikila, Ukukumana, ukupanga ubutantiko, amafya, ukubomba. 
## Ico cishinka nakuma Coordinators, Distributors, Agents elyo nakuli bonse abo abaibimbilemo mukushitisha kwa “Natuleya!”. 
## Twatotela bonse pa kuibimbamo kwabo! Nakucilishapo twatotela Shifwe uwa mumulu uyo uwatwafwa ukulemba, ukupanga nokuleta kuli imwe nayambi yatatu ama magazine ya “Natuleya!”.
## Kabili tulefwaya ukutasha bamunyinefwe ne nkashi sha mu Germany abo batwafwilishe ukucilika ifipunda ifyo twatwalilile ukukwata muli uyu mwaka wacibili uwa “Natuleya!”. 
## Akasebo ka ndalama kapelwe kwibumba lya Natuleya kalangisha ukuti umwaka wafumako icipendo ukushinta nakuli 7,722 ica ma magazine (ukubikapofye na “Imishila ya Cisumino Cesu”) calishitishiwe nangu ukutumwa ukufuma kwi Ofeshi lyesu. 
## Lelo kwaletwafye indalama shama magazine 2,419. 
## Ici cipendo ca 31% ico ciletulangisha ukutila imishitishishe yesu tailileko pantanshi pakati ka 2009 na 2010, nobukulu bwacipunda nakabili bwafikile ku K12,000,000.
