## “Natuleya!” ya kuntanshi
## Muli uno mwaka tulinokumona ukuya kwa ba Editor balipo.
## Lesa alebatungulula pamo nolupwa lwabo ukubwelelamo ku Germany uko bali nokuibimba muku kansha kwa ntungulushi sha munkuta nefya buminshoni.
## Ici tacishile mukupumikisha, lelo kukwambafye bamunyinefwe abaibimbamo balyesha ukushimpa uyu mulimo munshila iwingakonkanyapo nokubomba pa myaka iingi ukwabula ukushintilila pa muntu uuli
onse uleutungilila. 
## Lelo fyonse fibili, ukulolesha kunuma elyo nakuntanshi, 
## nacilenga intungulushi sha uyu mulimo ukutontonkanyapo bwino bwino nokutantika ifintu fimo ifilingile ukucinjishiwa pakuti magazine ingatwalilila kuntanshi.
## Nanomba tatulakumanisha bamunyinefwe nenkashi isha uyu mulimo.
## Pamulandu waici, casuminishiwe ukusankanya amabumba yabili, ilya lelolekesha pali “Natuleya!” elyo nelya “Inkosho”.
