## Lelo mufifulo tulefwaya ukubika bambi, mukwai moneni ilyashi pebula 30.
## Tulekabila ukusha ubusuma bwa magazine kuli bakabelenga.
## Kukusenamina kwakwa Lesa, bamunyinefwe aba mu Germany balilenga twakwanisha ukushita mashini iikalamba kabili iyangufyanya ukuprinta amapepala. 
## Ngefyo mumwene magazine ili muminwe yenu, ilekwanisha ukuprinta pepepala ilikulu (A3), kabili nefikope filemonekako bwino nomba.
## Pakuti twingabikamo amalyashi yalekana lekana, twakulapanga amagazine aya mundimi shibili, imo mu Cibemba imbi nayo mu Cingeleshi. 
## Icikasha incende yakubikapo amalyashi nayambi muli cila lulimi. 
## Elyo twalikonka nefyo bakabelenga bamo bamo batwebele ukutila twingasansha “Natuleya!” ne “Ikosho” nokukwatafye magazine imo kuntanshi lelo isuma. 
## Kuli abo baleumfwa bwino sana ukubelenga magazine iikwete indimi shibili bakakonkanyapo ukuilako pantanshi mukusambilila ukupitila mukushita yonse yabili – amalyashi ayengi yakatwalilila ukuba cimo cine.
## Tulekabila ukubweshako umutengo wakupangila.
## Umutengo wamapepala, inki nemweseshe ilenina inshita yonse. 
## Pantu tulefwaya kutuula imilimo mu lubali lwa milembele, ukutwala mululimi lumbi, nemipangile ya magazine pamabeya ya bantu abengi, tulekabila ukufushishako indalama ishakubomfya.
## Ilangi lya nkupo nga iyi ili mumwinwe yenu isenda indalama ukufika kucipendo 45% ishacipendo tupangila. 
